OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirefighters face sack for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbullying or racist         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbehaviour                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Firefighters face the sack if they are 
OL,6, found to have bullied or been racist,  
OL,7, misogynistic or homophobic, London Fire
OL,8, Brigade's boss said.                   
OL,10,FCommissioner Andy Roe made the comments
OL,11,Fafter an independent review found the  
OL,12,Fbrigade was "institutionally misogynist
OL,13,Fand racist".                           
OL,15,FThe review detailed accounts ranging   
OL,16,Ffrom women being groped to people      
OL,17,Fhaving their helmets filled with urine.
OL,19,FThe review was ordered after a fireman 
OL,20,Ftook his own life in August 2020.      
